      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-differential. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Recent major service includes a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve adjustment, ensuring the high-compression valvetrain operates with factory precision. While the exterior shows honest character from spirited road use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making it a purist's specimen ready for the apex.",
