      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the trunk tell the story of its road experience. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and clean, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. All technological features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a rigorous adherence to its service schedule. We have kept a comprehensive folder of all maintenance records, ensuring peace of mind for the next owner. This car drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers the dependable performance you expect from a well-cared-for machine. It is a solid, reliable choice for anyone seeking a high-quality pre-owned vehicle that looks and feels great on the road.",
